    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "adm_startup_t",
      "x": 916, "y": 198, "width": 610, "height": 60,
      "text": "supports = isinstance(model, MultimodalModelMixin) AND processor capability\nexplicit tokens → strict; unset → max(LLM fallback, model atomic maximum)\ncapacity hook → Qwen: max(1, tokens / merge_unit); Pixtral/Mistral: min(items, tokens)\nprofiling → effective budget 안에서 long-item + many-item boundary를 순차 실행",
      "originalText": "supports = isinstance(model, MultimodalModelMixin) AND processor capability\nexplicit tokens → strict; unset → max(LLM fallback, model atomic maximum)\ncapacity hook → Qwen: max(1, tokens / merge_unit); Pixtral/Mistral: min(items, tokens)\nprofiling → effective budget 안에서 long-item + many-item boundary를 순차 실행",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 800018,
