      "x": 1180, "y": 790, "width": 350, "height": 60,
      "text": "max_num_items ← encoder_max_batch_size\n기본: Capacity → full-request 검사 / select(fitting)\n      → MicroBatch\n독립: select(active) → Capacity\n      → eligible 교집합 → MicroBatch",
